'''睡眠性交症'''（sleep sex、sexsomnia）是一種患者在[[睡眠|睡眠]]中進行[[人類性行為|性行為]]的症狀，属于[[睡眠異常|睡眠異常]]。在一些極端案例中，睡眠性交症會導致[[性騷擾|性騷擾]]甚至[[強姦|強姦]]的發生。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-20340562 | work=BBC News | title=Sleep: Weird things people do in their sleep | date=28 November 2012 | accessdate=2015-03-15 | archive-date=2017-12-15 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171215041127/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/magazine-20340562 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-south-east-wales-20758315 | work=BBC News | title='Sexsomnia' claim actor Simon Morris guilty of raping girl | date=17 December 2012 | accessdate=2015-03-15 | archive-date=2019-04-28 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190428162659/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-wales-south-east-wales-20758315 | dead-url=no }}</ref> 這種病症發現時間並不長，但已經引發了數起案件。<ref name="psychologytoday" /><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20140920/36096690/ | publisher=蘋果日報 | title=稀奇「睡眠性交症」 夢遊性侵竟無罪 | date=2014-09-20 | accessdate=2015-03-15 | archive-date=2017-04-30 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430024448/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/international/20140920/36096690 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

==病因與治療==
睡眠性交症可能與[[夢遊症|夢遊症]]、[[睡眠呼吸中止症|睡眠呼吸中止症]]、[[夢驚|夢驚]]和[[尿床|尿床]]並發，原因可能是生活壓力過大、[[睡眠剝奪|睡眠剝奪]]或[[酗酒|酗酒]]、滥用药品等。<ref>{{cite web |title=Sexsomnia |publisher=Sleep.com |url=http://www.sleep.com/content/sexsomnia |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140122133100/http://www.sleep.com/content/sexsomnia |archivedate=2014-01-22 }}</ref><ref name="psychologytoday">{{cite news |title=Sexsomnia |url=http://www.psychologytoday.com/blog/sleepless-in-america/200902/sexsomnia |work=Psychology Today |year=2009 }}</ref> 這種病症在患者獨處時也許看不出來，但可能會因在睡眠中接觸床伴而觸發。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Trajanovic NN, Mangan M, Shapiro CM |title=Sexual behaviour in sleep: an internet survey |journal=Soc Psychiatry Psychiatr Epidemiol |volume=42 |issue=12 |pages=1024–31 |date=December 2007 |pmid=17932612 |doi=10.1007/s00127-007-0258-0}}</ref> 實際上患者本人未必知道自己患有這種病症。[[氯硝西泮|氯硝西泮]]可用來治療此症。<ref>{{cite journal|author=Shapiro CM, Trajanovic NN, Fedoroff JP |title=Sexsomnia—a new parasomnia? |journal=Can J Psychiatry |volume=48 |issue=5 |pages=311–7 |date=June 2003 |pmid=12866336 |url=http://ww1.cpa-apc.org:8080/Publications/Archives/CJP/2003/june/shapiro.asp |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100210022052/http://ww1.cpa-apc.org:8080/Publications/Archives/CJP/2003/june/shapiro.asp |archivedate=2010-02-10 }}</ref><ref>A patient treated with clonazepam was featured on the television documentary ''[[Strange_Sex|Strange Sex]]'' that aired on TLC 27 January 2010</ref>

== 歷史==
關於睡眠性交症的第一份研究由[[多倫多大學|多倫多大學]]和[[渥太華大學|渥太華大學]]的三位研究人員發表于1996年。<ref>{{cite journal |author=Shapiro CM, Fedoroff JP, Trajanovic NN |title=Sexual behavior in sleep: a newly described parasomnia |journal=Sleep Research |volume=25 |pages=367 |year=1996 |url=http://www.websciences.org/cftemplate/NAPS/archives/indiv.cfm?ID=19960381 |access-date=2015-03-15 |archive-date=2009-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090429212510/http://www.websciences.org/cftemplate/NAPS/archives/indiv.cfm?ID=19960381 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 1998年美國的一名神經學家大衛·索爾·羅森菲爾德（David Saul Rosenfeld）報道了來自[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]地區的、美國最早的睡眠性交症（當時稱為“sleepsex”）案例。<ref>{{cite journal|pmid=9604116 | volume=27 | issue=3 | title=Sleepsex: a variant of sleepwalking |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-sexual-behavior_1998-06_27_3/page/269 |date=June 1998 | author=Rosenfeld DS, Elhajjar AJ | journal=Arch Sex Behav | pages=269–78|doi=10.1023/A:1018651018224}}</ref> 醫學上所用的術語“sexsomnia”由科林·夏皮羅（Colin Shapiro）于2003年6月的一個病例中首次使用。<ref>{{cite journal |title=Sexsomnia – A New Parasomnia? |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_canadian-journal-of-psychiatry_2003-06_48_5/page/311 |author=Shapiro CM, Trajanovic NN, Fedoroff JP |pmid=12866336 |journal=[[Canadian_Journal_of_Psychiatry|Canadian Journal of Psychiatry]] |volume=48 |issue=5 |date=June 2003 |pages=311–7}}</ref>

